* greet_lib.sno — library that exports GREET
* LP-4 acceptance test (M-LINK-NET-3)
* Convention: exported symbol name matches file base → IMPORT SNOBOL4.GREET
* Assembly produced: SNOBOL4_Greet_lib.dll  method: GREET
